@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xuaokn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.52)) - ((tmp + 0.46 / v2 + 0.72) / 0.75))
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.24)) + wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.89)))
    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.98 / v1 + 0.71) * (v2 + 0.78 - tmp + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
